---
layout: base.njk
title: Living Posts
description: Posts that evolve and improve over time.
---
<section class="card">
  <h1>Living Posts</h1>
  <p>
    These posts are intentionally alive. They grow through revisions, updates, and
    new context as the work evolves.
  </p>
</section>

<section>
  {% if collections.posts | length %}
    <ul class="stack-list">
      {% for post in collections.posts %}
        <li class="card">
          <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
          <p>{{ post.data.excerpt or "No excerpt yet." }}</p>
          <p class="meta-inline">
            Published {{ post.date | prettyDate }} |
            Last updated {{ (post.data.lastUpdated or post.date) | prettyDate }} |
            Revisions {{ post.data.revisionCount or 1 }}
          </p>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  {% else %}
    <p>No living posts yet.</p>
  {% endif %}
</section>
